    3) Run (F5) to debug locally.

    Publish:
    - Use Properties/PublishProfiles/*.pubxml or Visual Studio Publish wizard.
    - Confirm runtime identifier matches chosen platform when using dotnet publish.

    Maintenance checklist:
    - Add .gitignore that excludes bin/, obj/, .vs/, and user files.
    - Do not edit generated files under obj/; regenerate by cleaning and rebuilding.
    - Keep project TFM and SDK versions in CITY#ZERO.csproj up to date.
    - Maintain a top-level Inventory.md or manifest (recursive file list + optional SHA256 hashes) for agent verification.

    Next recommended tasks:
